comments: Gobert (UTA) grabs and pulls Robinson-Earl's (OKC) jersey, impeding him near the rim.
Conley (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Dort (OKC) and the contact is incidental.
Dort (OKC) has an arm extended in Mitchell's (UTA) path but the marginal contact does not affect his SQBR.
Robinson-Earl (OKC) avoids making any contact that affects Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt as Mitchell slips the contact on his way to the basket.
Giddey (OKC) brings his arms forward but the marginal contact does not affect Mitchell's (UTA) shot attempt near the rim.
Dort (OKC) drives into Gobert (UTA) and dislodges him from his defensive position.
O'Neale (UTA) moves along with Giddey (OKC) on the perimeter and the body contact is marginal.
Conley (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Giddey (OKC) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
